The files included are as follows:

	Makefile - Makefile with the following targets:
		default: builds the executable lab4b using lab4b.c source code
		check: quick smoke test to test if lab4b can handle all options and basic stdin command
		clean: removes executable and tarball from pwd
		dist: builds tarball lab4b-604970765.tar.gz

	lab4b.c - source code to build the executable; includes the following options:
		--scale - changes the scale to Farenheit or Celsius, Farenheit by default
		--period - changes the number of seconds between samples. By default: 1
		--log - specifies a file to log samples and console commands to
